text: Español de Cádiz was a football team from Cádiz, Andalusia. They played in Andalusia Championship between 1915 and 1928. Their best performances was to win Andalusia Championship (:es:Copa de Andalucía) in the first edition of 1915-1916. http://footballpresscuttings.blogspot.com.es/ http://www.rsssf.com/tabless/span-surchamp.html http://elcorreoweb.es/historico/definido-el-diseno-de-la-renovada-copa-de- andalucia-KAEC718604 Español de Cádiz had the right to play in 1916 Copa del Rey after winning Andalusia Championship 1915-1916 http://footballpresscuttings.blogspot.com.es/2015/03/campeonato-de- andalucia-1915-16.html but they did not inscribe for the tournament. ==References== Category:Cádiz Category:Defunct football clubs in Andalusia
